        "text": "Leviticus 27:16",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). It was of considerable length (according to the Talmud about 48 ft.) and was passed round the body several times (Jos. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Ant.",
