        "text": " iii. 7. 2). It seems to have been accidentally omitted in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Exodus 29:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". It must be distinguished from the ‘cunningly woven band of the ephod’ (cp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
